#: 00826:7
msgid "Maybe I could use this opportunity to patch things up with Hinata-san."
msgstr "Quizá sea una buena oportunidad de llevarme mejor con Mizuki."

#: 00826:8
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Will you be my partner, Hinata-san?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Puedes ser mi compañera, Mizuki?\""

#: 00826:11
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Huh? M-me?!\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¿¡Yo!?\""

#: 00826:12
msgid "Hinata-san seemed really surprised. I wonder if she'll refuse?"
msgstr "Parece muy sorprendida."

#: 00826:15
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"I guess......\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Supongo...\""

#: 00826:16
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Yes!!\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¡¡Sí!!\""

#: 00826:17
# Entiendo que se refiere a chocar el puño con la mano en plan: ¡Lo he conseguido!
msgid "Before I knew it I started pumping my first in the air."
msgstr "Antes de ser consciente, ya estaba chocando el puño."

#: 00826:22
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"Wow, you're happy.\""
msgstr ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"Vaya, si que estás contento.\""

#: 00826:23
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I thought she was going to turn me down.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Pensaba que iba a rechazarme.\""

#: 00826:30
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"What made you think that?\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"¿Qué te hace pensar eso?\""

#: 00826:34
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"What did you do to her?\""
msgstr ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"¿Qué es lo que le hiciste?\""

#: 00826:35
msgid "Everyone thinks I did something to upset her."
msgstr "Todos se piensan que le hice algo malo."

#: 00826:38
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"There's nothing between us.\n"
"We've hardly even talked before.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"No hay nada entre nosotros.\n"
"Apenas hemos hablado antes.\""

#: 00826:45
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"That's the thing. You guys sit next to each other everyday and you guys don't talk at all.\""
msgstr ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"Ese es el problema. Os sentáis juntos todos los días y no os habláis para nada.\""

#: 00826:52
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Kazushi, you didn't suddenly try to go after Mizuki-chan, did you?\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"Kazushi, ¿la has agredido o algo?\""

#: 00826:53
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Are you guys crazy?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Estáis locos?\""

#: 00826:57
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"But still, it's clear there's something between you two. Mizuki-chan pays extra attention to you.\""
msgstr ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"Pero es obvio que Mizuki que trata de forma diferente.\""

#: 00826:61
# ¿Es? ¿Está?
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"She is......?\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"¿Ella está...?\""

#: 00826:65
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"You are, Mizuki?\""
msgstr ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"¿Lo estás, Mizuki?\""

#: 00826:68
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"I'm not, I'm not! Why do I have to pay any attention to Haruma-kun?\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¡Claro que no!\n"
"No hay absolutamente nada entre nosotros, ¿vale?\""

#: 00826:69
# No hace falta que me rechaces con tanta energía...
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"You don't have to deny it so forcefully...\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No hace falta que lo niegues tan enérgicamente...\""

#: 00826:70
msgid "It hurt to hear her deny it so clearly."
msgstr "Ha sonado como si estuviese enfadada conmigo."

#: 00826:76
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"Don't be so disappointed, Kazushi.\""
msgstr ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"No estés tan decepcionado, Kazushi.\""

#: 00826:81
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"She dumped you, Kazushi. It's nothing to be that upset over, though.\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"Buen intento Kazushi, pero parece que no tiene absolutamente ningún interés por ti.\""

#: 00826:82
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Why do you guys always have to make fun of me when you're supposed to be providing encouragement?\""
msgstr ""

#: 00826:89
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"I didn't say anything...\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Yo tampoco he dicho eso...\""

#: 00826:90
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"You're fine.\n"
"It's best to just say \"no\" when you're not interested.\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"Si lo has hecho bien.\n"
"Es mejor decir que \"no\" cuando no estás interesada.\""

#: 00826:91
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Don't worry about me!\n"
"I'm used to being rejected!\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¡No te preocupes por mí!\n"
"¡Ya estoy acostumbrado a que me rechacen!\""

#: 00826:97
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"He's used to getting rejected......\n"
"Poor Kazushi-kun.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Acostumbrado a que le rechacen...\n"
"Pobre Kazushi.\""

#: 00826:102
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"Don't worry, Haruka.\n"
"Kazushi has me.\""
msgstr ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"No te preocupes, Haruka.\n"
"Kazushi me tiene a mí.\""

#: 00826:105
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"What?\n"
"You guys are......?\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"¿Qué?\n"
"¿Estáis...?\""

#: 00826:112
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"What? You're already two-timing?!\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"¿¡Qué!?\n"
"¿¡Desde cuando!?\""

#: 00826:113
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"That's not true!\n"
"I don't know anything about what she just...\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¡Eso no es verdad!\n"
"No sé que está diciendo...\""

#: 00826:116
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"It's fine. A man has to be a bit of a player in order to feel like a big-shot.\""
msgstr ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"No pasa nada Kazushi.\n"
"Puedes contarlo.\""

#: 00826:120
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"Wow, Ran-chan, how understanding! You're a good woman!\""
msgstr ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"Vaya Ran. Vas muy directa.\""

#: 00826:124
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Wait a minute.\n"
"Are you guys serious?\""
msgstr ""

#: 00826:125
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Calm down, you guys.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Tranquilizaos.\""

#: 00826:126
msgid "This joke is getting out of hands."
msgstr "La broma se está desbocando."

#: 00826:132
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"...\""

#: 00826:133
msgid "Hinata-san was getting upset for being left out."
msgstr "Mizuki ha acabado mosqueada por esperar a que terminásemos de hablar."

#: 00826:136
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Hey, Kazushi!\n"
"Are we going to start working or what?\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Eh, Kazushi,\n"
"¿Vamos a hacerlo o no?\""

#: 00826:137
msgid "She sounded seriously annoyed."
msgstr "Parece realmente mosqueada."

#: 00826:138
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Yes, we are!\n"
"Please!\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Sí, ¡claro!\n"
"¡Por favor!\""

#: 00826:139
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Well, then, why don't we get started?\n"
"I don't like those who dawdle and can't make up their minds.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Bueno pues, ¿qué tal si empezamos?\n"
"No me gusta estar haciendo la tonta.\""

#: 00826:140
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Yes!\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¡Sí!\""

#: 00826:141
msgid "I think I just gave her another reason to get annoyed at me."
msgstr "Creo que acabo de darle otro motivo para estar enfadada conmigo."

#: 00826:145
msgid ""
"{Mei}\n"
"\"I'm glad you're all having fun, but please remember that we're still in class.\""
msgstr ""

#: 00826:146
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I'm sorry...\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Lo siento...\""

#: 00826:148
msgid "I got scolded by the teacher. Now I need to put some effort into this and create a good result."
msgstr "No solo Mizuki, también la señorita Ibuki está enfada."

#: 00826:151
msgid ""
"{Principal}\n"
"\"Hu-hu......\""
msgstr ""
"{Directora}\n"
"*Sonriendo*"

#: 00826:152
msgid "The principal was the only one who was smiling. Well, I'll do my best!"
msgstr "La directora era la única sonriendo. Está bien, ¡lo haré lo mejor que pueda!"

#: 00826:156
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"The procedure is the same as last time, right?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Como la última vez, ¿vale?\""

#: 00826:159
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"That's right. This in the flask, then light the burner.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Está bien.\n"
"Pon el frasco la fuego.\""

#: 00826:161
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Got it.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Entendido.\""

#: 00826:162
msgid ""
"Just put the supplies in the flask and turn on the flame.\n"
"A child can do this."
msgstr ""
"Ponr los materiales en el frasco y encender el fuego.\n"
"Hasta un niño podría hacerlo."

#: 00826:163
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Remember, controlling the heat is the most important part, so watch it closely, OK?\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Y recuerda, ajustar el fuego es la parte más importante, ¿entendido?\""

#: 00826:164
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"All right.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Entendido.\""

#: 00826:165
msgid "She was telling me what to do, but sounded rather cold and distant. I need to show her my good side too."
msgstr "Me dice lo que tengo que hacer, aunque noto su tono algo frío."

#: 00826:166
msgid "I think the flame was set about this high..."
msgstr "Creo que la temperatura debería llegar hasta aquí."

#: 00826:169
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"...\""

#: 00826:170
msgid "I guess this is good. Hinata-san's upset, so I'm afraid to ask."
msgstr "No dice nada. Espero que eso signifique que está bien."

#: 00826:174
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Turn the heat up a little bit.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Sube un poco la temperatura.\""

#: 00826:175
msgid "Haruka helped me out from the sidelines."
msgstr "Haruka vino a ayudarme."

#: 00826:176
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"A bit higher?\n"
"Like this?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Un poco más?\n"
"¿Así?\""

#: 00826:178
msgid "I turned the flame up a bit."
msgstr "Subí el fuego un poco más."

#: 00826:179
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Yep, that's it. Watch the inside and keep adjusting it. The color will change as the synthesis progresses.\""
msgstr ""

#: 00826:180
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Oh! There you go.\""
msgstr ""

#: 00826:181
msgid "The ingredients were starting to combine and turn black."
msgstr "Los ingredientes se están mezclando y convirtiéndose en una masa negra."

#: 00826:184
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Yeah, looks like you're doing good. You have to adjust it as the color keeps changing. If it doesn't go smoothly, there's a high chance of failure.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Así es.\n"
"Debería cambiar el color un par de veces más.\""

#: 00826:185
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"You really know your alchemy!\""
msgstr ""

#: 00826:188
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Thanks. I grew up learning this. Oh, turn up the heat.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Gracias. Crecí aprendiéndolo.\""

#: 00826:189
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Oh!\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¡Ah!\""

#: 00826:191
msgid "I adjusted the heat and the color changed again. I was always bad at chemistry and found it boring, but this is kind of fun."
msgstr "Ha vuelto a cambiar de color."

#: 00826:195
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"..................\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"...\""

#: 00826:196
msgid ""
"Oops.\n"
"I forgot that Hinata-san was my partner, not Haruka."
msgstr ""
"Ups.\n"
"Me he olvidado de que mi compañera era Mizuki y no Haruka."

#: 00826:197
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Umm...A-are we doing okay so far?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Lo estamos haciendo bien por ahora?\""

#: 00826:198
msgid "I tried talking to her."
msgstr "Traté de hablar con ella."

#: 00826:201
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"I don't know.\n"
"Why don't you ask Haruka.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"No sé.\n"
"¿Por qué no le preguntas a Haruka?\""

#: 00826:203
msgid ""
"Ouch.\n"
"I think she's upset. Shit."
msgstr ""
"Ups...\n"
"Parece que está mosca."

#: 00826:206
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Oh no!\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Ohm no...\""

#: 00826:207
msgid "Haruka's eyes reflected her disappointment as she looked at the flask."
msgstr "Haruka mira al frasco decepcionada."

#: 00826:209
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What......?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Qué...?\""

#: 00826:211
msgid "Crack..."
msgstr "*Frasco derritiéndose*"

#: 00826:214
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"No......\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"No...\""

#: 00826:217
msgid "The flask began to crack, and the liquid inside started spilling out."
msgstr "El frasco se ha roto y el líquio de dentro se ha acabado desparramando por toda la mesa."

#: 00826:218
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I guess this means we failed?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Hemos fallado?\""

#: 00826:219
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Looks like it.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Pinta tiene.\""

#: 00826:220
msgid "It was over quickly."
msgstr "Ha terminado enseguida."

#: 00826:221
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Why did that happen?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Cómo ha pasado?\""

#: 00826:226
msgid ""
"{Principal}\n"
"\"The god of alchemy is actually a goddess.\n"
"If you make the girl you work with upset then the alchemy will fail.\""
msgstr ""
"{Directora}\n"
"\"El Dios de la Alquimia es en realidad una diosa.\n"
"Si enfadas a tu compañera, no funcionará.\""

#: 00826:227
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Huh? Is that so... The goddess of alchemy?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Ya veo...\""

#: 00826:230
msgid ""
"The principal was still smiling.\n"
"I'm not sure if she just had a jab at my failure or if she's serious about the goddess effect."
msgstr ""
"La directora sigue sonriendo.\n"
"No estoy seguro si está mofando de mi fracaso o si decía en serio lo del efecto de la diosa."

#: 00826:231
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I failed because I made Hinata-san upset?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿El motivo del fracaso fue enfadar a Mizuki...?\""

#: 00826:234
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"What? It's not my fault.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"¿Qué quieres decir?\n"
"No es culpa mía.\""

#: 00826:235
msgid "I made her angry again. I still lack discipline."
msgstr "Sigo enfadándola."
